01.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dramaqueen.com.tw%2Ffeatures%2F20181015%2F001.html&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=9682b89a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/features/20181015/001.html</a> &lt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 集集都有鬼出現<br />\n故事聚焦自小在美國一棟知名鬼屋長大的五位手足，描述其中四位兄弟姊妹在成年後，因最年幼的妹妹自殺而在這棟房子重聚。不久後超自然現象接踵而來，影響了他們的心智，也迫使他們面對自我的過往。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=9bce4fad\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2df73510\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4033101bde2c4f633dc339f3725eb4ed84ad2767","tid":870091,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T20:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a126314850265ce305e72bfe9c650a5b02c9f2b","tid":870091,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53144e74ff4bdabeca954a04eb7faac9ca1071f6","tid":870091,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"